body:
I&#039;m loving the new system, but I&#039;m hoping that it&#039;ll be expanded so I can honor more teammates. So far, I&#039;ve had a few games where almost everyone worked together and had fun. Trying to decide on a single person to honor felt a bit counter-intuitive. 

I know that this may lower the value of each honor, but players who are consistently good teammates will still be rewarded. It feels rare for only one player to stand out in such a team-based game, so it would be great if everyone could get the glory.
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
